{
  "info": {
    "name": "Contextual News Data Retrieval System",
    "description": "A complete collection for the Inshorts News Retrieval API. Covers all 7 endpoints: LLM-driven query, category, score, search, source, nearby, and trending feed.\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:8080\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Run the Spring Boot app: `JAVA_HOME=$(/usr/libexec/java_home -v 21) mvn spring-boot:run`\n2. Set `GEMINI_API_KEY` env variable for real LLM summaries\n3. Use the collection variables below to switch base URL easily",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "inshorts-news-api-v1"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Base URL of the running Spring Boot application"
    },
    {
      "key": "defaultLimit",
      "value": "5",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🤖 LLM Query (Natural Language)",
      "description": "POST /api/v1/query\n\nThe main entry point. Send a plain English query. The LLM extracts entities + intent, routes to the right retrieval strategy, and enriches results with AI summaries.\n\nRequires GEMINI_API_KEY to be set.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Query — Nearby (with location)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"query\": \"Latest developments near Mumbai\",\n  \"userLat\": 19.0760,\n  \"userLon\": 72.8777,\n  \"radiusKm\": 50,\n  \"limit\": 5\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/query",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "query"]
            },
            "description": "LLM detects intent: 'nearby'. Routes to the nearby endpoint using user coordinates."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
